  "description": "Relocation of multiple gas facilities to accommodate infrastructure improvements.",
  "enriched_description": "Gas infrastructure relocations to accommodate NCDOT road widening projects including Memorial Drive, Allen Road (U-5875), Evans Street (U-2817), 14th Street (U-5917), and Firetower Road. Budget expanded from original $5.2M to $9.5M as NCDOT timelines firm up. These relocations precede major corridor improvements that will enhance commercial access and property values along growth corridors. Related to GUC's strategy of proactive infrastructure positioning for regional development. Watch for coordination with NCDOT construction schedules.",
